solution:
```class Solution {
    public String resultingString(String s) {
        while (s.length() > 1 && isConsecutive(s.charAt(0), s.charAt(1))) {
            s = s.substring(2);
        }
        return s;
    }

    private boolean isConsecutive(char a, char b) {
        return Math.abs((b - a) % 26) == 1;
    }
}```
